{"id":17486,"date":"2019-05-27T21:32:50","date_gmt":"2019-05-27T14:32:50","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=17486"},"modified":"2019-06-20T22:30:08","modified_gmt":"2019-06-20T15:30:08","slug":"cach-su-dung-google-analytics-track-affiliate-link","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/usecase\/cach-su-dung-google-analytics-track-affiliate-link","title":{"rendered":"C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Google Analytics \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i link affiliate"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\">\u0110a s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft <strong>c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Google Analytics<\/strong> \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i ph\u00e2n t\u00edch l\u01b0\u1ee3ng traffic website c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng \u00edt b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng Google Analytics \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i xem c\u00f3 bao nhi\u00eau ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5m v\u00e0o link affiliate tr\u00ean website.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Affiliate lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n thu nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c blogger \u0111\u1ec1u mong mu\u1ed1n. Khi blog b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 traffic t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng \u0111o l\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7t link affiliate, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd r\u1ee3i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng bao nhi\u00eau. B\u1edfi v\u00ec th\u00f4ng qua vi\u1ec7c theo d\u00f5i link affiliate b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 GI\u00c1N TI\u1ebeP \u0110O L\u01af\u1edcNG CH\u1ea4T L\u01af\u1ee2NG N\u1ed8I DUNG B\u00c0I VI\u1ebeT c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u00ec v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u theo d\u00f5i link affiliate b\u1ea1n c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh vi kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ecdc gi\u1ea3 tr\u00ean website c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh <strong>bi\u1ebft<\/strong> <strong>c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Google Analytics \u0111\u1ec3 track link affiliate tr\u00ean to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/strong>, b\u1ea1n c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft th\u00eam c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o b\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 lu\u00f4n b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh website.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ea1n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n theo h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o b\u1ea1n \u0111ang d\u00f9ng giao di\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfng Anh (<em>n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng giao di\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfng Anh s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n sau n\u00e0y h\u01a1n trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf<\/em>). N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang d\u00f9ng giao di\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t th\u00ec h\u00e3y chuy\u1ec3n sang giao di\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfng Anh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>V\u00e0o&nbsp;<strong>Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n<\/strong><\/li><li>Ch\u1ecdn tab&nbsp;<strong>D\u1eef li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n ho\u00e1<\/strong><\/li><li>K\u00e9o xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ebb&nbsp;<strong>T\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn chung cho web<\/strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef<\/strong>&nbsp;&gt; English (United State)<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/thay-doi-giao-dien-tieng-Anh.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"518\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/thay-doi-giao-dien-tieng-Anh-1024x518.png\" alt=\"Thay Doi Giao Dien Tieng Anh\" class=\"wp-image-17928\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/thay-doi-giao-dien-tieng-Anh-1024x518.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/thay-doi-giao-dien-tieng-Anh-218x110.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/thay-doi-giao-dien-tieng-Anh-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/thay-doi-giao-dien-tieng-Anh-700x354.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/thay-doi-giao-dien-tieng-Anh-768x389.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/thay-doi-giao-dien-tieng-Anh.png 1433w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Chuy\u1ec3n sang giao di\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi plugin Google Analytics m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ch\u00e8n code th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng Google Analytics hay Google Tag Manager th\u00ec s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang. Khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn n\u00e2ng cao kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng nguy\u00ean l\u00fd l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1eebng lo l\u1eafng, khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nguy\u00ean l\u00fd th\u00ec c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng plugin hay kh\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n quan tr\u1ecdng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>1. Ch\u00e8n m\u00e3 Universal Google Analytics v\u00e0o website<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ch\u00e8n m\u00e3 tracking code c\u1ee7a <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Google Analytics (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/analytics.google.com\/analytics\/web\/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Google Analytics<\/strong><\/a>, khi b\u1ea1n copy v\u00e0 paste l\u1ea5y \u1edf Admin Setting l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang d\u00f9ng Global Site Tag (<em>gtag.js<\/em>).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y Universal Google Analytics (<em>analytics.js<\/em>) b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i copy ID v\u00e0 d\u00e1n v\u00e0o code sau. (<em>Thay UA-XXXXX-Y b\u1eb1ng ID c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/em>)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&lt;!-- Google Analytics -->\n&lt;script>\n(function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){\n(i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o),\nm=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[0];a.async=1;a.src=g;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m)\n})(window,document,'script','https:\/\/www.google-analytics.com\/analytics.js','ga');\n\nga('create', 'UA-XXXXX-Y', 'auto');\nga('send', 'pageview');\n&lt;\/script>\n&lt;!-- End Google Analytics --><\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00e1 phi\u1ec1n ph\u1ee9c khi b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a r\u00e0nh c\u00e1ch ch\u00e8n m\u00e3 v\u00e0o website ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng n\u00e0o.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t plugin mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/plugins\/google-analytics-dashboard-for-wp\/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Google Analytics Dashboard for WP (GADWP)<\/strong><\/a>&nbsp;l\u00e0 xong.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Xem th\u00eam&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"\/client\/knowledge-base\/module\/cai-dat-google-analytics\/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t Google Analytics Dashboard for WP (GADWP)<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. C\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 Google Analytics c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft khi n\u00e0o c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5m v\u00e0o link affiliate c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i h\u00e0nh vi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng, Google Analytics s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o event. Nh\u01b0ng&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8230;Event l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Event l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch Google hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng b\u1ea5m v\u00e0o link n\u00e0o, download g\u00ec, b\u1ea5m xem video n\u00e0o, g\u1eedi form n\u00e0o t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o b\u00e1o c\u00e1o th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea cho b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng b\u1ea5m v\u00e0o link affiliate s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o event nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang. <strong>Plugin Google Analytics Dashboard for WP (GADWP) s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o event cho Google Analytics t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng (v\u00ec v\u1eady B\u01b0\u1edbc 1 v\u00e0 2 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng)<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1ch c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh Google Analytics Dashboard for WP (GADWP) nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>B\u1eadt <strong>tracking affiliate<\/strong> <strong>links<\/strong><\/li><li>Chuy\u1ec3n link affiliate sang d\u1ea1ng link <strong>Affiliate<\/strong> <strong>regex \/out\/<\/strong><\/li><li>\u0110\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u &#8220;<strong>use hitCallback to increase event tracking accuracy<\/strong>&#8221; (\u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng g\u1eedi data si\u00eau t\u1ed1c 100ms \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 s\u1edf d\u1eef li\u1ec7u Google Analytics gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 track nhanh v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n)<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/cau-hinh-Google-Analytics.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"875\" height=\"542\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/cau-hinh-Google-Analytics.png\" alt=\"Cau Hinh Google Analytics\" class=\"wp-image-17915\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/cau-hinh-Google-Analytics.png 875w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/cau-hinh-Google-Analytics-218x135.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/cau-hinh-Google-Analytics-300x186.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuo